<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.6">
<l>miṭaṟu meḻumeḻut tōṭa veṇṇey viḻuṅkip pōy</l>
<l>paṭiṟu palaceytip pāṭiyeṅ kumtiri yāmē</l>
<l>kaṭiṟu palatiri kāṉata riṭaikkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>iṭaṟaveṉ piḷḷaiyaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him from wandering everywhere in this village</l>
<l rend="indent">going around, devouring butter so that it runs softly [down his] neck,</l>
<l>committing many misdeeds,</l>
<l>I sent my child stubling after the calves on the forest path</l>
<l rend="indent">where many elephants wander.</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
